column1: 1. Khalnayak gachyal jungle madhye god gondhal karun zop ghetoy.
2. Garib lokana gaurav asava he changla guna aahe, khunas karun garva thevayla nako.
3. Changla jevan, chamakdar kapde ani god zaga milali tar jindagi khushkhabar aahe.
4. Jungle madhye jiraf, gondas ani guni jivant aslyamule jivsrushti chamatkar aahe.
5. Khunas karayla ghabrat aslelya khalnayak la shevti jeet milali nahi.
6. Gadhul gharat god zaga shodhun, guni lokanni jimmedar jagrut rahile pahije.
7. Jamin varil jivanu jeernoddhar karnyasathi jaivik ghol vaparataat.
8. Joshane bharlelya jawan lokana jimkhana madhye jeet milali.
9. Jamin varil jalpralayane ghor ghanerda jhalela.
10. Jungle madhye god jaga shodhun, garib lok zop ghet hote.
11. Changla jevan, chamatkar jadu ani god gungat jhalyasarkhe vatle.
12. Khunasacha khulas khushkhabar asel tari garib lokana nyay milala pahije.
13. Jahir zalela ghor khunas pahila, garib lok ghabrat hote.
14. Jungle madhye, guni shikari, jiraf shikar karnyasathi, god jaga shodhtoy.

16. Ghor khunas ghungat madhye jhala, khalnayak god zaga shodhun potachala.
